### 4. JSON Output Format
**File**: [prompt_generator.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/prompt_generator.py)

When [character_bible](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/narrative_review.py#679-704) is present, AI outputs structured JSON:

```json
{
  "scene": { "action", "era", "location" },
  "characters": [
    { "label", "ref_type": "cref/sref", "action", "uniform"... }
  ],
  "setting": { "architecture", "environment", "key_props" },
  "atmosphere": { "lighting", "mood", "weather", "effects" },
  "camera": { "shot", "angle", "focus" },
  "flat_prompt": "complete text prompt"
}
```

